1.0.0.name: wordpress/wp-ultimate-email-marketer
1.0.0.description:
WP Ultimate Email Marketer is a ultimate email marketing plugin to create, send, schedule, track, automate and analyse your email marketing campaigns. More than that it extends further as

  1. Contact Management
  2. List/Group Management
  3. Subscribtion Management
  4. Auto Prospects follow ups
  5. Email click throughs
  6. Statistics

The free version of Ultimate Email Marketing Plugin have limitations on features and for a maximum of 500 mails/day can be sent. Upgrade to pro version to enjoy all fully functional features as described above without any limitations.

Support and Feature request.

Please create issues only in our tracker support instead of WordPress support forum.

For guides and tutorials, visit Here.<
